Although Figure 25 illustrates the overall means for the different Reserves, when the data is clustered, three groups are apparent.
Group 2 represents the Reserves indicating that funding is a high priority in every a category of need while the other two groups have less needs or were able to better distinguish their priorities (Table 18).
