Grand Bay NERR, Mississippi This is an annual Marine Education Festival that we sponsor for all age groups but especially K-8.
We have approximately 40 booths set up by local resource agencies that address coastal issues and students K-12th participate in a scavenger hunt of coastal facts at each of the booths.
The schools that send the highest percentage of their students win a monetary award to buy science materials for their school.
