North Carolina NERR, North Carolina A Coastal Exploration provides some general activities for use in the classroom as well as some basic information about Estuaries and their importance.
Teachers and educators learn about North Carolina's 2 million acres of estuaries and their importance in our seafood industry; general ecological concepts; and impacts on estuaries.
